name: Sunset 74feet Teak Outdoor Loveseat
details: Exaggerated scale and dramatic angles create midcentury appeal with a distinctly modern twist from the fresh design minds at Fred Segal. Weather-resistant fabric tailors the seat and back cushions of this outdoor loveseat in a relaxed linen-like neutral. When left uncovered, the loveseat will patina to a beautiful silvery grey
